f(t+\Delta t, x+h)
f(t+\Delta t, x)=f(t,x) + \Delta t \cfrac{\partial f}{\partial t}(t,x)+(\Delta t)^2 \cfrac{\partial^2 f}{\partial t^2}(t,x) + O((\Delta t)^3)
f(t, x+h)=f(t,x) + h \cfrac{\partial f}{\partial x}(t,x)+h^2 \cfrac{\partial^2 f}{\partial x^2}(t,x) + O(h^3)
u=(t,\,x),\;\; \Delta{u}=(\Delta{t},\,h), \;F(\lambda)=f(u+\lambda\Delta{u}) \;\;(\lambda\in \mathbb{R}).
